.DS_Store

# Trained model artifacts (rebuilt locally by `python main.py --mode train`).
# These are environment-specific pickles: a model saved on a NumPy 2.x machine
# CANNOT be unpickled on the Windows 7 / NumPy 1.x live box (raises
# "No module named 'numpy._core'"). Never commit them; train on the target box.
models/*.pkl
models/*.h5
models/*.joblib
models/*.incompatible
!models/.gitkeep
